{"tid":2309746,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嬉皮士文化討論","createTime":"2020-12-02T18:18:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T11:43:14.000Z","uid":29969,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d786880d8f2f251fbed74f1c04fca5f079c44823","tid":2309746,"uid":29969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T18:18:13.000Z","msg":"見中文既圈冇乜呢個討論<br />\n上網搵到既關於中文解釋都比較少<br />\n之前都唔知呢個文化係咩黎<br />\n直到睇左條片<br />\n發覺嬉皮士文化同自己價值觀好相同<br />\n所以睇下有冇人可以討論下<br />\n<br />\n前設講完<br />\n其實嬉皮士講既係peace and love<br />\n呢樣野本身係好既<br />\n我認為人類最終都應該要係咁<br />\n但係喺呢個講求經濟物質既社會好難做到<br />\n所以對某啲人嚟講係天方夜譚<br />\n就好似環保撚咁本質係好<br />\n但要做何其容易呢<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/M9JGcz3j9-k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FM9JGcz3j9-k&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOXejezXkYyU2Z26LisGJHUw%3D&h=c63383fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/M9JGcz3j9-k</a>"},{"pid":"0f93f685d3fc81b99bf476f0f4b6ec54276288a9","tid":2309746,"uid":29969,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T18:19:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ebcc33224fc7c0243408ac669c4f5c92b164826","tid":2309746,"uid":29969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T18:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d1946482472fd4844bf052f63503ccf8ffdb38","tid":2309746,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T18:22:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"112a2d3294850cd303ec8a7b9d5b4618b5dc5b18","tid":2309746,"uid":29969,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"27d1946482472fd4844bf052f63503ccf8ffdb38","tid":2309746,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T18:22:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T18:23:42.000Z","msg":"開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開返學術台先<br />\n我個人偏右<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor